Amir Khan has added to his collection of top-of-the-range cars with a brand new white Mercedes S63, which he has shown off on social media. 

The boxer posted three images to his Twitter account of himself stood in front of the new motor, wearing his brand of clothing and posing with a trademark clenched fist. 

Khan took to his social media account to show how pleased he was with his new purchase, writing: 'Finally got my hands on the #S63'.

