Khan is a known car enthusiast and the new addition to his garage will accompany a Bentley Continental, a Mercedes CLS63, Audi R8 and two Range Rovers.

The S63 retails at around £100,000 and is capable of reaching 60 mph in just 4.2 seconds.

Khan is looking for a fight later this year against Floyd Mayweather Jnr, who last month posted a picture with his eight supercars and £30m private jet for good measure.

